黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-size: 16px;\">赏茶器：银制托盘骨瓷茶具</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">点心 ：食用顺序司康饼咸味三明治巧克力水果果浆黄油</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">品茶：格雷伯爵茶正山小种大吉岭茶阿萨姆奶茶水果红茶柠檬</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 600; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, SimSun, 宋体, sans-serif; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;; font-size: 16px;\">伯爵茶的由来做个悬念，先看看红茶是怎么来的。（品饮格雷伯爵）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 22.484375px; outline: none; table-layout: fixed; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51